# üß™ Virtual Probing ‚Äì HostHunter

üîó **HostHunter ‚Äì Official GitHub Repository**  
https://github.com/SpiderLabs/HostHunter

**HostHunter** is a Python-based reconnaissance tool designed for **Virtual Host (VHOST) discovery and probing**.  
It helps identify multiple domains hosted on the **same IP address**, which is especially useful in **shared hosting environments**.

---

## üéØ Use Cases

- üß≠ Identify virtual hosts associated with a single IP address  
- üïµÔ∏è Discover hidden or undocumented domains on shared infrastructure  
- üöÄ Expand attack surface during reconnaissance and penetration testing  

---

